headline: OnTrac challenges FedEx, UPS with cross-country delivery services

headline: ConData Appoints Chris Cassidy as Chief Executive Officer
summary: CHICAGO, September 09, 2025--ConData, a leading provider of global freight post-audit and supply chain spend management and analytics services, today announced the appointment of Chris Cassidy as Chief Executive Officer. Backed by Astira Capital Partners, ConData is entering an important new chapter as it continues to expand its technology-enabled solutions and strengthen its role as a trusted partner in the global supply chain ecosystem.
